To compile:

- Optional: Edit lightserver.c
- Put lightserver.c and SConstruct in the rpi_ws281x directory
- run: scons -Q
- open_lightsocket is the executable

To run the SERVER:
- sudo /path/to/open_lightsocket
- Use "-h" to see options

To run the CLIENT:
- python /path/to/lightclient.py
- Use "-h" to see options
- e.g. python lightclient.py -d 5 -r 3